Urban Glitch series

This is about the human dynamics at the city, and the way it creates new forms, in the "non-lieux", forms that don't really physically exists.

This is the only record that remains of these photographs, in the form of .gif, the .jepg that were used to build it disappeared when the laptop (where the original files were stored) was stolen from me.
